
=== Fantastic Slideshow ==
Contributors: Fantastic Slideshow
Tags: slideshow, slider, carousel, slides, responsive
Stable tag: 1.0

Easy to use and versatile slideshow with layout and styling customizations. 


== Description ==
Easy to use and versatile slideshow with layout and styling customizations.  Responsive and supports image and text links.
Change the slideshow speed, fade in speed, add a pause/play button, and more.  


== Installation == 
1. Upload the 'fantastic-slideshow' folder in '/wp-content/plugins' directory.
2. Activate the plugin in the Plugins menu in WordPress.


